sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as ClientA / ClientB
  participant API as Protected API
  participant SSO as SSO Server
  participant R as Redis

  C->>API: Request with expired access_token
  API-->>C: 401 Unauthorized

  Note over C: Response interceptor starts refresh
  C->>SSO: POST /token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token<br/>refresh_token, client_id, client_secret

  SSO->>SSO: verifyRefreshToken(refresh_token)
  SSO->>R: GET session:{sessionId}
  SSO->>SSO: Validate token match + client_id match

  SSO->>SSO: Generate new access_token + rotate refresh_token
  SSO->>R: SET session:{sessionId} (new refreshToken, TTL)
  alt session has device binding
    SSO->>R: SET deviceSession:{deviceType}:{deviceId} = sessionId (TTL)
  end

  SSO-->>C: 200 {access_token, refresh_token, token_type, expires_in, scope}

  Note over C: Update local session/token store
  C->>API: Retry original request with new access_token
  API-->>C: 200 OK

  alt refresh failed
    SSO-->>C: 400/401 invalid_grant or invalid_client
    C->>C: Clear local session and force re-login
  end